link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/mastercard-scholarship-at-united-states-international-university-africa-usiu-africa\/#Method_of_Form_Submission\" title=\"Method of Form Submission\">Method of Form Submission<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82274758\">Mastercard Scholarship at United States International University Africa, USIU Africa<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82274759\">Summary of Scholarship:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82274760\"><strong>Scholarship Eligibility\/Criteria<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82274761\"><strong>Offered Benefits<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82274762\">Duration of Award:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82274763\">Method of Application<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82274764\">Method of Form Submission<\/a><\/p>\n<h3 id=\"summary-of-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Summary_of_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82274759\"><\/a>Summary of Scholarship:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Qualification:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Diploma, Bachelor<\/p>\n<p>Deadline:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 01-Oct-2024<\/p>\n<p>Country:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Africa<\/p>\n<p>Value:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Full Scholarship, Laptop, Stipend<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"scholarship-eligibility-criteria\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Scholarship_EligibilityCriteria\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82274760\"><\/a><strong>Scholarship Eligibility\/Criteria<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Only\u00a0youth not exceeding 29 years old in the following categories are qualify:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Young women and men.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Refugees and displaced youth of Africa;<\/li>\n<li>Youth with disabilities (special consideration).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"offered-benefits\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Offered_Benefits\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82274761\"><\/a><strong>Offered Benefits<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>The Mastercard Foundation Scholars at USIU-Africa will receive holistic support which includes:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tuition and functional fees;<\/li>\n<li>Laptops, books, and other learning materials;<\/li>\n<li>Accommodation and meals;<\/li>\n<li>Medical Insurance;<\/li>\n<li>Stipend;<\/li>\n<li>Logistics.<\/li>\n<li>Full Access to Leadership Training sessions;<\/li>\n<li>Access to Entrepreneurial Training courses;<\/li>\n<li>Psycho-social support, career counseling and mentorship programs;<\/li>\n<li>Disability needs will be reasonably catered for.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"duration-of-award\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Duration_of_Award\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82274762\"><\/a>Duration of Award:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>4 years<\/p>\n<p><em><strong>Read Also&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/nursing-scholarships-to-study-in-australia-us-and-canada\/\">10% Free Sponsorship Nursing Scholarships to study in Australia, US and Canada<\/a><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"method-of-application\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Method_of_Application\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82274763\"><\/a>Method of Application<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Do you wish to apply?<\/p>\n<p><span class=\"td_btn td_btn_md td_3D_btn\" style=\"background-color: #000000;\"><strong><a style=\"background-color: #000000;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.usiu.ac.ke\/mcf-scholarship\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Download the\u00a0Application Form.<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<h3 id=\"method-of-form-submission\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Method_of_Form_Submission\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82274764\"><\/a>Method of Form Submission<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>After filling the downloaded forms, applicants should endeavor to submit completed application forms by email as an attachment to\u00a0<a href=\"mcfsp-applications@usiu.ac.ke\u00a0\">mcfsp-applications@usiu.ac.ke\u00a0<\/a>or drop their application at Admissions Office, located in the Main Administration building at USIU Africa, or post copies of the application forms to:<\/p>\n<p><strong>Program\u00a0Director,<br \/>\nMastercard Foundation Scholars Program,<br \/>\nUnited States International University \u2013 Africa,<br \/>\nP. O. Box 14634 \u2013 00800, Nairobi \u2013 Kenya<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Mastercard Scholarship at United States International University Africa, USIU Africa. This is to announce that the application for&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":18446,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[984],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1268"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1268"}]